lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Johanna Konta advanced to the semifinals of the Elite Trophy by beating Caroline Garcia 6-2, 6-2 on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Top-Seeded Konta Beats Garcia to Advance at Elite Trophy
